{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"baa4123ffb","title":"“班三角还有民主吗？”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c046fbe0c3","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"baa4123ffb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"5b08996b26","name":"热风"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0108668c9a","type":"title","text":"“班三角还有民主吗？”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"dca63bf2e4","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院热风","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"c898ef5932","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角，不民主，谁领导，党小组。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"fdbeea6a60","type":"paragraph","text":"班长由院长任命，代表行政总揽班上大权。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"b701f4e06d","type":"paragraph","text":"团支书只代表班上团员，但一切都得由他指点。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"fabd41653c","type":"paragraph","text":"学生代表是同学选，但只把文娱活动来管。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"137a2d6436","type":"paragraph","text":"选举权吧！同学们只有一遍。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"daaaad64be","type":"paragraph","text":"团员选了学生代表还有支书特权。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"9c9d860a90","type":"paragraph","text":"党员更不用说，在班上有他的领导权。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"eee4448171","type":"paragraph","text":"学校、系上有要事都把班长来喊。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"2dca74af08","type":"paragraph","text":"另外还有党团组织干部参加提意见。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"198337ba1e","type":"paragraph","text":"学生代表有职无权却在一边。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"bf6f501f6e","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角、官僚机构干部成团。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"143547d4b1","type":"paragraph","text":"有干事有组长还有板报编辑员。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"032682a5a5","type":"paragraph","text":"开会时党小组领导，支委参加占人数一半。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"616bb5d61e","type":"paragraph","text":"官多兵少，事难办，剩下摊子无人管。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"f27b9268c2","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角之优越性，不知如何体现。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"f43fa83ef8","type":"paragraph","text":"这是生硬照苏联把教条来搬。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"c63dcd8156","type":"paragraph","text":"建议立即取消，采取班委由同学来选。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"e62368830d","type":"paragraph","text":"既民主，工作又好办。(热风第二期)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"},{"id":"200aa54ffd","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb"}],"page":{"id":"ddadc82e0c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"baa4123ffb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}